<section id="features">
<div class="row">
<h2>Features</h2>
<ul id="features-grid">
<li class=" medium-6 large-4 columns text-center pretty-tile">
<div class="feature-tile">
<div class="tile-text">
<img src="https://light.co/content/2-camera/1-features/1-test1/web_icons-15.png" alt=""> <h6 class="tile-header">Massive 52-megapixel resolution</h6>
<p class="tile-subheader">Every memory captured in exquisite detail.</p>
<p class="tile-content">The L16 produces extraordinarily high-quality photos. Think: striking details, better colors, and significantly less noise. More than 52 megapixels gives you the creative freedom to zoom, crop, and enlarge to your heart&rsquo;s content.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class=" medium-6 large-4 columns text-center pretty-tile">
<div class="feature-tile">
<div class="tile-text">
<img src="https://light.co/content/2-camera/1-features/2-test2/web_icons-03.png" alt=""> <h6 class="tile-header">Over 5x optical zoom</h6>
<p class="tile-subheader">Let your camera get up close and personal for you.</p>
<p class="tile-content">As you zoom in or out, the L16 intelligently chooses the best combination of 28mm, 70mm, and 150mm camera modules for your scene. That way, you can get intimate without getting close.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class=" medium-6 large-4 columns text-center pretty-tile">
<div class="feature-tile">
<div class="tile-text">
<img src="https://light.co/content/2-camera/1-features/3-precise-depth-of-field-control/web_icons-01.png" alt=""> <h6 class="tile-header">Precise depth-of-field control</h6>
<p class="tile-subheader">Make your subject stand out.</p>
<p class="tile-content">With our state-of-the-art software, your creative control doesn&rsquo;t have to stop when you take the photo. Lumen allows you to adjust depth-of-field and give your image as much or as little of that natural background blur as you wish.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class=" medium-6 large-4 columns text-center pretty-tile">
<div class="feature-tile">
<div class="tile-text">
<img src="https://light.co/content/2-camera/1-features/4-automatic-over-the-air-updates/web_icons-07.png" alt=""> <h6 class="tile-header">Software that improves over time</h6>
<p class="tile-subheader">A smart camera that keeps getting smarter.</p>
<p class="tile-content">The L16 is built on a software platform much like your smartphone. With every wireless update we deliver, your camera will get better, faster, and more powerful. You&rsquo;ll see the difference.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class=" medium-6 large-4 columns text-center pretty-tile">
<div class="feature-tile">
<div class="tile-text">
<img src="https://light.co/content/2-camera/1-features/5-convenient-size/web_icons-08.png" alt=""> <h6 class="tile-header">Convenient size</h6>
<p class="tile-subheader">Capture more, carry less.</p>
<p class="tile-content">You need a camera that fits your lifestyle. The compact L16 is light enough to leave your camera bag behind and small enough to slide right into your back pocket, so that you never have to miss a special moment.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class=" medium-6 large-4 columns text-center pretty-tile">
<div class="feature-tile">
<div class="tile-text">
<img src="https://light.co/content/2-camera/1-features/6-join-the-image-revolution/capture_4x.png" alt=""> <h6 class="tile-header">Join the image revolution</h6>
<p class="tile-subheader">Capture photos in a radically new way.</p>
<p class="tile-content">With 16 different lenses behind a flat face, the L16 looks like something out of this world&mdash;and it is. Meet the camera of the future. Our groundbreaking technology is changing photography as we know it, and you can be a part of it.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</div>
</section>



